00:25:05.630 --> 00:25:10.580
But several things take
place, one, hiring in bundles.

00:25:10.580 --> 00:25:12.880
Those of us who are
here from industry

00:25:12.880 --> 00:25:16.250
understand that initial classes
which come into organizations

00:25:16.250 --> 00:25:18.330
tend to be more diverse.

00:25:18.330 --> 00:25:21.930
But that diversity doesn't carry
forward as we move people up

00:25:21.930 --> 00:25:23.100
