00:25:33.730 --> 00:25:36.370
What would you like for dessert?

00:25:36.370 --> 00:25:37.590
Pecan pie.

00:25:37.590 --> 00:25:41.450
If I ask you to fill out
a calendar for every lunch

00:25:41.450 --> 00:25:44.300
and every dinner for
the next 12 months,

00:25:44.300 --> 00:25:46.840
will you only choose pecan pie?

00:25:46.840 --> 00:25:48.020
Of course not.

00:25:48.020 --> 00:25:49.574
When people are
hiring in bundles

00:25:49.574 --> 00:25:50.990
