00:25:53.080 --> 00:25:55.240
But when people are
hiring for one offs,

00:25:55.240 --> 00:25:57.510
they tend to want what
their favorite is.

00:25:57.510 --> 00:25:59.770
Favorite is a
substitute word for what

00:25:59.770 --> 00:26:02.110
Allison talked
